\end_layout

\begin_layout Section*
24.
 Lorentz transformation of the fields
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section*
12.
 Invariant Cross-section
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Number of collisions is conserved because you can think of each collision
 as one point in the space, and the point maps uniquely via the lorentz
 transformation.
\end_layout

